Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveA cousin of former President Goodluck Jonathan Mike Ogiasa Kidnapped June 1 at Otuogidi, Ogbia, Bayelsa, is having a hell of time in the grip of his captors.
He was at a point bound up, and lowered into a grave filled with debris, from where he cried for help, according to a video shared by journalist, Jackson Ude on Twitter.
The state police command have yet to speak on the report and efforts it’s making to secure Ogiasa’s release.
